      "value": "<p>As Shouchite no Jutsu, but the hand is Large, has a Strength score of 35 and a base attack bonus equal to half your level, and can reach out to grapple an adjacent enemy once per round. While successfully grappling, a successful grapple check deals 2d6+12 damage to the grappled creature as the hand crushes it. The hand has a Defense of 20 (10, -1 size, +11 natural) and has 2 HP per level.</p>\n\n\n\n",
